Popular Nigerian comedian, Mr. Macaroni has revealed he has no plan of getting married soon. Macaroni made this known during a question and answer session via his Twitter page. When asked if he’s considering marriage anytime soon, Mr. Macaroni said ‘no’. According to him, marriage scares him and he has not been in a relationship since 2012. His tweet read: “No! Marriage scares me. I haven’t been in a relationship since my time in Houdegbe North American University, Benin Republic (HNAUB). That’s like 2011-2012.” Macaroni also disclosed that he attended four universities: Leads City, Houdegbe North American University and Babcock before he finally graduated from Redeemers University.